  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and sauté until softened, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add the ginger garlic paste and stir for 1-2 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin powder, coriander powder, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper. Stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lemon juice and stir for 1-2 minutes, until the mixture thickens slightly.",
    "Add the shrimp and stir to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 5-7 minutes, or until the shrimp are pink and cooked through.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot."
